  "prompt": "If you call someone on whatsapp by mistake and instantly hang up, does it still give them a missed call notification?",
  "response": "If you call someone on WhatsApp by mistake and hang up immediately, it typically still registers as a missed call on their end. The notification will depend on their app settings and device, but generally, a missed call notification will be sent to the recipient. If you're concerned about this, you might consider sending a quick message to apologize for the accidental call.",
